last_episode_to_air.name: Making Mama Proud
last_episode_to_air.overview: Tyler invites his former co-star Hannah Brown to help design his neighbor's primary suite. As Mom's house speeds toward completion, Tyler focuses on creating the backyard entertaining paradise she always wanted. An open house shows off the stunning results for all friends and family. Life and laughter have returned to Mom's house.

name: Going Home with Tyler Cameron
overview: Reality TV star and former The Bachelorette heartthrob Tyler Cameron follows his dream of starting his own construction and home renovation company.

episodes.name: Welcome Back, Tyler
episodes.overview: After the sudden loss of his mother, Tyler Cameron returns to his hometown of Jupiter, FL to reconnect with his family, fulfill his Mom's dream of renovating the family home, and launch his own dream of starting a construction company, Image One. Though their budget is small, Tyler & Co aim to wow their first client, a recently-engaged professional couple seeking to upgrade their first home.

episodes.name: The Customer Is Always Wright
episodes.overview: Off to a solid start, Tyler and Image One take on their next project, one that comes with a new set of challenges that have him juggling a larger home remodel and high maintenance clients. Meanwhile, Tyler and his brother Ryan begin the tough task of clearing out Mom's house to prepare for the big renovation.

episodes.name: The Ex's Condo
episodes.overview: When Tyler’s high school girlfriend becomes Image One's next client, the pressure to deliver an amazing renovation increases. At Mom's house, Tyler seeks out a family friend for design advice and plans one last hurrah at his childhood home before work begins.

episodes.name: Cameron Brothers vs Pops' House.
episodes.overview: Tyler and Robb do a favor for a neighbor and are rewarded with a commission to turn a generic garage into a sports car showroom. Meanwhile, Tyler plans a surprise for Pops to thank him for his help. Tyler and his brothers band together to do a stealth renovation of Pops' house while Pops is out of town.

episodes.name: Say Uncle
episodes.overview: Tyler convinces his aunt and uncle to hire Image One to renovate their multi-million dollar home. But dear Uncle Howie turns out to be Tyler's toughest client yet, and Aunt Michelle wants the work done before Christmas. The deadline proves painstaking as Tyler fields constant change orders to satisfy their wishes and keep the peace. At Mom's house, Tyler and his two brothers begin renovations.

episodes.name: Big Money Gamble
episodes.overview: Tyler prepares to host a gala to raise funds for a charity that his family recently founded in his mother's name. Meanwhile, Tyler brings in a surprise investor to turn a run down house into a sweet short term rental. Costly termite damage soon forces Tyler to find alternative ways to bring his vision of a beachy staycation to life. But will it be enough to impress his new partner?

episodes.name: Dude, Where's My Hut Tub?
episodes.overview: Image One is busier than ever. Mom’s house is underway and Tyler's highschool friend wants to turn his first home into the ultimate bachelor pad. He's got big dreams for the small house and the project quickly grows in scope. When a third project falls into Tyler's lap, Tyler reaches out to an old flame for help.
